---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms and Conditions" description="Terms and Conditions for NETSums.">
  <section class="py-20 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-white mb-2">Terms and Conditions</h1>
      <p class="text-sm mb-8" style="color:#94a3b8">Last updated: January 11, 2023</p>

      <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 p-8 flex flex-col gap-6" style="background-color:#132d52; color:#94a3b8">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Company</h2>
          <p>Ricardo Carvalho, c/o Block Services, Stuttgarter Str. 106, 70736 Fellbach, Germany</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Acknowledgment</h2>
          <p>You must be over 18 to use this Service. By accessing it you accept these Terms and the Privacy Policy.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Links to Other Websites</h2>
          <p>NETSums is not responsible for the content, privacy policies, or practices of any third-party websites.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Termination</h2>
          <p>We may suspend your access immediately without prior notice for any breach of these Terms.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>Liability is capped at the amount paid or $100 USD maximum. We exclude special, incidental, indirect, or consequential damages.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Governing Law</h2>
          <p>These Terms are governed by German law, excluding conflict of law rules. EU users benefit from mandatory consumer protections in their country.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Changes to Terms</h2>
          <p>We reserve the right to modify these Terms with 30 days' notice for material changes.</p>
        </div>

        <div>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-2">Contact</h2>
          <p>
            <a href="mailto:contact@netsums.com" style="color:#5ce1e6">contact@netsums.com</a>
            {' '}or via the{' '}
            <a href="/contact" style="color:#5ce1e6">contact form</a>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
